name: Nuclear Powerhouse
title: Leading Nuclear Energy Producer
description: In 2023, France generated 64.17% of its electricity from nuclear sources, making it one of the top producers of nuclear energy worldwide.

name: Education Excellence
title: Top Female Primary Education Enrollment
description: As of 2016, France achieved a 99.65% adjusted net enrollment rate for female primary school children, showcasing its commitment to gender equality in education.

name: Safe Haven
title: Minimal Internally Displaced Population
description: In 2022, France reported only 10 internally displaced people, reflecting its stable socio-political environment.
